reviews.review_text: I came for the SHAKEDOWN but stayed because of Estimated, Wharf Rat, etc The shakedown here has gotten its just kudos- but the rest of the show lingers in the shadow of that funk beast- but it should not- I am going to boldly say that the Estimated outro jam here is one of the finest of its kind- and the wharf rat? A top ten contender on its own merit- In fact- a true rarity occurs before jer's first true to me solo- you can here him say, after "true to me"..."Here we go"- talking during a song? wow!!crispy playing in evidence all nite- and well worth the download
Great show Huge East Coast energy really seems to drive the band.
